## 2. UI/UX Design (The Checkout Screen)

The user's registered phone number is pre-filled but editable (in case they want to pay from a different Airtel number).

```text
====================================
           CHECKOUT
====================================
Delivery To: 123 Cairo Road (15 mins)
Total to Pay: K150.00
------------------------------------
PAYMENT METHOD:

 ( ) Cash on Delivery (COD)

 (*) Airtel Money
    ---------------------------------
    | +260 | 097 123 4567         | X |  ← Pre-filled, editable
    ---------------------------------

====================================
