```text
[ USER TAPS "PLACE ORDER" ]
         |
         v
POST /api/v1/orders  →  Order created (PENDING_PAYMENT), inventory reserved
         |
         v
POST /api/v1/orders/{id}/pay  →  Airtel STK Push sent
         |
         +-- Airtel API Error  →  UI: "Couldn't reach Airtel. Try COD."
         |                        (order still exists, can be cancelled cleanly)
         |
      PUSH_SENT
         |
    [ UI: "Waiting for PIN..." ]
         |
    (Polls /payment-status every 3s)
         |
-------------------------------------------------
|                        |                      |
[ Webhook: TS ]   [ Webhook: TF/TA/TE ]   [ No webhook — 60s elapsed ]
|                        |                      |
CONFIRMED            CANCELLED            AirtelFailsafeScheduler queries Airtel
|                        |                      |
UI: Success!         UI: "Payment           TS → CONFIRMED
Redirect to          not completed"        TF/TA/TE → CANCELLED
Tracking             [Try Again]           Still in-progress → wait next cycle
                     [Use COD]
```

